<Layout title="Terms of Service | Glow Trading">
	<main>
		<h1>Terms of Service</h1>
		<section class="content">
			<p class="last-updated">Last Updated: December 14, 2023</p>

			<h2>1. Services Offered</h2>
			<p>LeanMaxx is a subscription-based calorie tracking application that uses artificial intelligence to simplify nutrition monitoring. Access is provided on a monthly subscription basis in United States Dollars (USD).</p>

			<h2>2. Customer Service</h2>
			<p>For support or inquiries, contact us at:</p>
			<p>Email: hi@glow.trading</p>
			<p>Phone: +1 (650) 456-0002</p>

			<h2>3. Refund Policy</h2>
			<p>We offer a 30-day money-back guarantee. If you're unsatisfied with our service, contact hi@glow.trading within 30 days of purchase for a full refund.</p>

			<h2>4. Data Privacy</h2>
			<p>We collect and store user phone numbers for account identification and security, as well as food entries for nutrition tracking functionality. Your data is securely stored and used solely for providing and improving our service.</p>

